title: Demand Greatness
itunes:title: Demand Greatness
description:
Episode 187 - How often do we settle for less than we can achieve instead of demanding absolute greatness from ourselves? In this episode I speak about a man named David Goggins who has been inspiring me like crazy lately and how it has affected my mindset.
